{
  "name": "Miraggio — Vendor Payment Confirmation Email",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📧 Vendor Payment Confirmation Email\n\n**Flow:**\nSupabase payments INSERT → Webhook → Extract Data → Fetch Bill+Vendor → Merge → Has Receipt? →\n  YES: Download → **Save to Supabase Storage** → **Update payments record** → Send Gmail WITH attachment\n  NO: Send Gmail without attachment\n\n**PDF Storage path in Supabase:**\n`receipts/confirmed/{invoice_number}_{payment_id}.pdf`\nVisible in: Supabase → Storage → receipts bucket → confirmed/ folder\n\n**Setup:** Supabase → Integrations → Database Webhooks → payments table → INSERT → POST to webhook URL",
        "height": 260,
        "width": 480,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
      "name": "📋 SETUP",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [-900, -260]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "miraggio-payment-confirmation",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-8901-bcde-f12345678901",
      "name": "Payment Webhook",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [-500, 0],
      "webhookId": "miraggio-payment-confirmation"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "// n8n wraps the full HTTP request — actual Supabase data is inside .body.record\nconst record = $input.first().json.body.record;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    bill_id:              record.bill_id,\n    vendor_id:            record.vendor_id,\n    payment_id:           record.id,\n    payment_mode:         record.payment_mode,\n    utr_or_cheque_number: record.utr_or_cheque_number,\n    amount_paid:          record.amount_paid,\n    paid_at:              record.paid_at,\n    paid_by:              record.paid_by,\n    receipt_url:          record.receipt_url || null,\n    receipt_filename:     record.receipt_filename || 'payment_receipt.pdf',\n  }\n}];"
      },
